{"tid":1339063,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突發、今次玩撚大左！","createTime":"2019-07-21T15:00:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T15:09:45.000Z","uid":268846,"like":3,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"59165a41ee93dbca58b5d8655d70973f1d13a87d","tid":1339063,"uid":268846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:00:54.000Z","msg":"國務院港澳辦，強烈譴責香港有示威者，圍堵中聯辦。<br />\n<br />\n發言人說，部分激進示威者圍堵中聯辦，向辦公大樓門口懸掛的國徽，投擲黑色油漆彈，在外牆噴塗侮辱字句，並試圖衝進辦公大樓。<br />\n<br />\n發言人說這種行徑，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">公然挑戰中央政府權威，觸碰一國兩制原則底線，性質嚴重，影響惡劣，絕對不能容忍，香港警方及時採取有關行動，非常必要。發言人又說，</span></span></strong>堅定支持特區政府依法採取一切必要措施，確保中央駐港機構安全，維護香港法治，懲治犯罪分子。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>屌，今次大陸真係有籍口做野，玩國徽，真係鬼佬都唔敢出聲⋯</strong></span>"},{"pid":"f8b39922c9bbbf26bc14e6ba1434b43b4a58e478","tid":1339063,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:01:35.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"a4915227c6bdc95e03f1d5b614e31893fe17440a","tid":1339063,"uid":82805,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:02:12.000Z","msg":"P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ef4471685442b2ec73982e827d9b44ba5404b8","tid":1339063,"uid":209355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:02:23.000Z","msg":"驚佢有味 打嘴炮佢就識 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a03f8f648fdea014d6cde52db209bf5e992c9f","tid":1339063,"uid":263012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:03:00.000Z","msg":"咁講0既話燒國旗HUR 國歌做左野好耐."},{"pid":"ce566028159a56d695a15199c12f790928995cd7","tid":1339063,"uid":262674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:04:10.000Z","msg":"屌咪又係果幾句 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5bb996fa290a822bdcbfa57f9b2f696ca8c1f3","tid":133